   </div>  <h1 class="article-heading" role="heading" itemprop="headline">How extreme isolation warps the mind</h1> <div class="information clearfix no-image">       <div class="author author-has-profile author-profile-collapsed ">   <div class="author-information story-meta no-image" itemprop="author">    <span class="arrow"></span>  Michael Bond </div>    <div class="author-profile toggle-content no-image">   <dl class="about">  <dt>About the author</dt>  <dd><p>Michael Bond is the author of The Power of Others (Oneworld Publications)</p></dd>  </dl>   </div> <script type="text/javascript"> require(["utils"],function(utils){ utils.toggleContent(); }); </script>   </div>       <ul class="tags"><!--   --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/sections/health" class="health" >Health</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/sections/science-environment" class="science" >Science &amp; Environment</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/tags/biology" class="tag" >Biology</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/tags/brain" class="tag" >Brain</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/tags/humanbody" class="tag" >Human body</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/tags/neuroscience" class="tag" >Neuroscience</a> </li><!--      --></ul>   </div>   <div class="social">       <!--[if lte IE 8]><span class="s-b-ie s-b-ie8"><![endif]--> <!--[if gt IE 8]><span class="s-b-ie s-b-iem"><![endif]--> <div class="s-b-container s-b-en-gb" data-version="0.4.1" data-variant="default" data-language="en-gb" data-ptrt="http://www.bbc.com/modules/share/close"> <div class="s-b s-b-default"> <form action="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/modules/share/page" method="get"> <input type="hidden" name="app_id" value="58567469885" id="sb-1-sb-1app_id"><input type="hidden" nam