ow-extreme-isolation-warps-minds&amp;title=&amp;" target="_blank" data-window-width="900" data-window-height="560" data-network="stumbleupon" tabindex="-1" class="s-b-p-a" title="Share this with stumbleupon"> <span> <i aria-hidden="true" class="gelicon gelicon--stumbleupon"></i> </span> StumbleUpon  </a> </li>  <li>  <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Fstory%2F20140514-how-extreme-isolation-warps-minds&amp;=&amp;" target="_blank" data-window-width="550" data-window-height="420" data-network="twitter" tabindex="-1" class="s-b-p-a" title="Share this with twitter"> <span> <i aria-hidden="true" class="gelicon gelicon--twitter"></i> </span> Twitter  </a> </li>  </ul> <a class="s-b-read-more" href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.co.uk/faqs/questions/bbc_online/sharing" tabindex="-1">Read more about these links.</a> <a href="#" class="s-b-p-close" tabindex="-1" title="Close"><i aria-hidden="true" class="gelicon gelicon--no"></i></a> </div> </div> <!--[if IE]></span><![endif]--> </div>  <div class="clearfix"></div>  <div class="lead-image"> <img itemprop="image" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/976_549/images/live/p0/1z/1z/p01z1zfd.jpg" alt="(Getty Images)" /> <p class="lead-image-caption">(Getty Images)</p>  </div>    </section> <section class="main-column clearfix"> <article class="story ">  <div class="body clearfix">     <div class="description" itemprop="description"> Our top 12 stories of 2014 - #6: When people are isolated from human contact, their mind can do some truly bizarre things, says Michael Bond. Why does this happen? </div>    <!-- RELATED ARTICLES -->  <aside class="related-articles small-icon"> <h3>Related</h3>    <article>  <div class="image-container"> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20130813-how-to-combat-loneliness-in-space"> <img width="144" height="81" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/144_81/images/live/p0/1f/22/p01f22n3.jpg" alt="How to combat the loneliness of space travel"></img> </a>      <div class="media-type-block">
