  </div>  <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20130813-how-to-combat-loneliness-in-space"><h5>How to combat loneliness in space</h5></a> </article>    <article>  <div class="image-container"> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20140505-secrets-behind-the-big-sleep"> <img width="144" height="81" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/144_81/images/live/p0/1y/jq/p01yjqsl.jpg" alt="(Thinkstock)"></img> </a>  </div>  <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20140505-secrets-behind-the-big-sleep"><h5>Can we ever hibernate humans?</h5></a> </article>    <article>  <div class="image-container"> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20140421-inside-the-minds-of-the-dead"> <img width="144" height="81" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/144_81/images/live/p0/1x/qw/p01xqwj4.jpg" alt="(Thinkstock)"></img> </a>  </div>  <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20140421-inside-the-minds-of-the-dead"><h5>Inside the minds of the dead</h5></a> </article>    <article>  <div class="image-container"> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20120719-awoken-from-a-2d-world"> <img width="144" height="81" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/144_81/images/live/p0/0w/88/p00w889v.jpg" alt="How a movie changed one mans vision"></img> </a>  </div>  <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20120719-awoken-from-a-2d-world"><h5>Awoken from a 2D world</h5></a> </article>    <article>  <div class="image-container"> <a href="/web/20150101114151/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20120807-the-loneliest-job-in-the-world"> <img width="144" height="81" src="/web/20150101114151im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/144_81/images/live/p0/0x/1h/p00x1hht.jpg" alt="Cold front"></img> </a>      <div class="media-type-block">
